<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="ash-n">ash <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /æʃ/    美 /æʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 灰；[复数] 灰烬：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>cigarette / volcanic ash 
香烟灰/火山灰</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The house burnt to ashes. 
房子烧成了灰烬。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[复数] 骨灰；废墟：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She wanted her ashes to be buried under the cherry tree. 
她希望自己的骨灰埋在樱花树下。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All her dreams had <strong>turned to ashes</strong>. 
她所有的梦想都化为泡影。</p></div></div>